category: CULINARY QUOTES
category comment: 

clue: Fran Lebowitz jokingly said, "My favorite animal is" this, but she didn't specify porterhouse or T-bone

response: a steak

clue: This breakfast goody has been described as "an unsweetened doughnut with rigor mortis"

response: a bagel

clue: Mark Twain said that cauliflower "is nothing but" this vegetable "with a college education"

response: cabbage

clue: This president said, "You can tell a lot about a fellow's character" by his way of eating jellybeans

response: Reagan

clue: Thackeray's "Ballad of" this dish calls it "a sort of soup or broth... or hotchpotch of all sorts of fishes"

response: bouillabaisse

